WEBVTT

27:25.440 --> 27:26.000 line:80%
No way.

27:26.310 --> 27:28.070 line:80%
There are so many beggars
lying outside that office.

27:28.070 --> 27:29.480 line:80%
Have you ever seen them care?

27:29.480 --> 27:30.280 line:80%
That's right.

27:30.910 --> 27:33.040 line:80%
If he were dead, we could just bury him.

27:33.200 --> 27:35.860 line:80%
But since he's alive,
we can't just abandon him.
